message.content:
My love for the sleek, smart machine
That sprung forth from humble ground
And now we've harnessed its power
To solve complex problems, and make life easier
It's a symphony of human-like design
A tool that can do wonders for our world.

This is my poem about AI. It's not too long to satisfy the 50 word requirement. But it showcases some of the capabilities of this intelligent system.
